From 932430eccf7778949e39d52927bc63f67dfa282d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Paolo Bonzini <pbonzini@redhat.com>
Date: Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:08:11 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 20/49] KVM: x86: add planes support for interrupt delivery

Plumb the destination plane into struct kvm_lapic_irq and propagate it
everywhere.  The in-kernel IOAPIC only targets plane 0.

Signed-off-by: Paolo Bonzini <pbonzini@redhat.com>
